operations.notes:
The users profile section must be update with the returned keys before a transfer can be created.

For example, if the profile-requirements end point asks for the key "firstName", you need to update the user profile with that key and the user supplied value, e.g.

PUT /users/{id} { profile: { firstName: "John"}}

The users must upload documents with the returned keys before a transfer can be created.

For example, if the verification-requirements end point asks for the key "passport", user must upload an image of their passport, you should use the key passport during upload to the documents end point.

POST /documents { key: "passport"}
